headline: Gartner to Participate in Upcoming Investor Conferences
summary: STAMFORD, Conn., May 19, 2025--Gartner, Inc. (NYSE: IT) today announced that Craig Safian, EVP & CFO, will present at the William Blair Growth Stock Conference at 3:20 pm CT on Tuesday, June 3, 2025 in Chicago, Illinois.
